      Why sponsor us?
    </h2>
    <p>
      As a foundation we are dependent on donations. By sponsoring us you will help us to continue achieving our goals and expand upon them. You will contribute to innovation, education, creating a learning environment and bringing like-minded people together. In addition to this your organization will get featured on our shirts, website, lab, social media, venues and more. And last but not least you get to connect with top tier, ambitious students in the field of AI and computer science for internships, working students and post graduate jobs.
    </p>
